 />\n同紫色樽果隻一樣用法？<br />\n<br />\n用緊紫色樽，真係冇味<br />\n但唔知點解有時會失效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次買呢隻黎試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98820f69ed72fd5d90d8b70907332d21d3e6611","tid":344710,"uid":47180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢幾個月差唔多日日都三十幾度，加上我又大汗，出一出街就好似倒水感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，想問吓各位巴打邊支止汗劑好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪理上面班傻鳩毒撚，又Nvieda 又adidas全部雙位數講咁多廢話都係要平啫，真係慘， 唔平都唔用，對佢哋來講最緊要夠平夠賤唔係講產品嘅實用性<br />\n我強烈推介依隻純天然草本<br />\nAesop 應該冇人唔識<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aesop.com/hk/body-care/personal-care/herbal-deodorant.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aesop.com%2Fhk%2Fbody-care%2Fpersonal-care%2Fherbal-deodorant.html&d=u%2F1HYRBVLHCuqs5ou2zj7Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8017fd43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.aesop.com/hk/body-care/personal-care/herbal-deodorant.html</a></blockquote><br />\n話人傻鳩毒撚之前<br />\n睇清楚樓主想要d 乜<br />\n佢係想要antiperspirant<br />\n你果支係deodorant, 唔止汗的"},{"pid":"bd1dae92a558b539f8e095dc3fc9dc35c01f03c6","tid":344710,"uid":47180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"不過antiperspirant都係唔好用咁多<br />\n驚有副作用"},{"pid":"328ff33ae8501010b49f12fc2644f97aa15ede4d","tid":344710,"uid":4510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"gatsby果隻海洋味幾正 噴落去好涼 陣味又唔太濃 但係又幾香 仲要一直keep住好涼好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b73770399767f38d922eec9b5a0fbd8c86741a7","tid":344710,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16